      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells brand new. I've babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and the paint is literally sparkling. It drives like a total dream! If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
