    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a benchmark example of the naturally aspirated 3.8L DFI flat-six, delivering 385 hp with surgical precision. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-optioned limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring and driver engagement. Meticulously maintained, the vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a lowered ride height and reinforced anti-roll bars for superior lateral stability. The braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors with four-piston monobloc calipers, showing zero fade or glazing. This specimen boasts a concours-level finish, documented service history with no bore scoring, and a pristine interior free of bolster wear. A mechanically flawless, turn-key investment for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
