    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem that defies its age, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings, while the original alloy wheels are entirely curb-rash free. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the dashboard is flawless, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-wallet policy at authorized service centers. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. This is a collector-grade example that includes all original keys, a complete set of owner's manuals, and a meticulously documented service history. It offers a tight, quiet, and powerful driving experience that feels as though it just rolled off the assembly line.",
